{"tid":1717203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家可唔可以回想吓，近幾日嘅唔同moment係諗緊啲咩？","createTime":"2019-11-13T14:16:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T17:15:30.000Z","uid":89898,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7089812f2088f7087baa2d34b154753f12fb9cf7","tid":1717203,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:16:06.000Z","msg":"短短一個禮拜發生咗好多事。保衛大學、癱瘓交通、中環lunch hour集會同法院first blood之類戰線有好大突破，同時我地都為好多事而嬲，疑似彥霖媽被自殺、梓樂死因存疑、第一城疑似打死人、警甴恐襲中大、畜牲性侵少女等等，呢個禮拜冇停過咁滯。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家可唔可以回想吓，近幾日嘅唔同moment係諗緊啲咩？<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n我怕嘅係，太多勇武畫面會令人有視覺疲勞，不論係咪同路人都係咁話，而太多支線任務會令大家不停被side track，要爭取嘅訴求，要雪嘅恥、要申嘅冤愈嚟愈多，好似慢慢遠離咗最原始嘅我地。<br />\n<br />\n所以，文宣係時候要再比多兩錢肉緊。每晚10點大嗌、airdrop文宣圖、update連儂牆、全港有連儂公廁、tg毒氣貼紙等等，麻煩大家做返足啲。<br />\n<br />\n大家寫出嚟放喺床頭又好轉做wallpaper又好，記住我地每日係為咗咩而奮鬥。唔打倒個不義嘅政權同制度，我地要嘅所有支線都唔會成功。記住由6月11號晚警甴已經要我地行刑咁搜身、6月9號晚港共已經已讀不回100萬民意、1997年中共已經準備陰乾香港。呢啲係所有真香港人不共戴天之仇。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>跟我講一次：五大訴求，缺一不可</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>跟我講一次：解散警隊，刻不容緩</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>跟我講一次：光復香港，時代革命</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>跟我講一次：天滅中共，全黨死清光</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n另外仲有四個字，就唔迫大家跟我講了。"},{"pid":"ac24e18d0870acf4f11078b74499b622ccc38b58","tid":1717203,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:17:03.000Z","msg":"每日臨瞓同我背默一次"},{"pid":"7445632b049c0d4e0dbce40a6e705920b6e24c7b","tid":1717203,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:17:13.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"445f8b0c64ed74f50c1bd5af3c3ead92cc28dd94","tid":1717203,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:17:23.000Z","msg":"解散警隊，刻不容緩"},{"pid":"52a6b41a4a744cb5673c2cd5880d46a275bd1cf6","tid":1717203,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:17:33.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"512e89bfc9d47ecab91d0a9afe3a4ff3b596d833","tid":1717203,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:17:43.000Z","msg":"天滅中共，全黨死清光"},{"pid":"e14966d1e8820dfcbea44ec8d3530e38686c60cd","tid":1717203,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:18:45.000Z","msg":"深個呼吸，抖一抖，繼續反抗！"},{"pid":"fefd1840e45453a38a3f8ed74e0b1b1b216992b2","tid":1717203,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:20:46.000Z","msg":"做咩都唔割，但求各位手足唔好畀情緒支配自己"},{"pid":"f06bdd400d8271bfec9610037496864fb4b1726e","tid":1717203,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:22:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1bccc8565c760da7d5c0eec07caf6a8d19a0910","tid":1717203,"uid":260429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:41:23.000Z","msg":"tg毒氣貼紙係點㗎"},{"pid":"e4549a9ff209ff979a9713e45d60172e9bb62267","tid":1717203,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1bccc8565c760da7d5c0eec07caf6a8d19a0910","tid":1717203,"uid":260429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:41:23.000Z","msg":"tg毒氣貼紙係點㗎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:36:37.000Z","msg":"本身老母深藍，自從睇到呢張文宣之後日日屌黑警<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1707648\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1707648</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea425b378427f0e68d009b03fc434a40b574d1f","tid":1717203,"uid":260429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4549a9ff209ff979a9713e45d60172e9bb62267","tid":1717203,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"